SELECT DISTINCT [t].[Distributor] AS [code], [t].[Distributor_Name] AS [name]

(DbType = Int32), @__date_Value_Date_4='?' (DbType = DateTime)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Tbl_ReviewAnswers] AS [t]
        WHERE [t].[Rscode] = @__RSCode_0 AND [t].[EmpNo] = @__EmpName_1 AND DATEPART(year, [t].[CreatedAt]) = @__year_Value_2 AND DATEPART(month, [t].[CreatedAt]) = @__month_Value_3 AND CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) = @__date_Value_Date_4) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
